This is Perl module App::watcher.

INSTALLATION

App::watcher installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

% cpan App::watcher

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

% perl Makefile.PL
% make && make test

Then install it:

% make install

DOCUMENTATION

App::watcher documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

% perldoc App::watcher
